import React from 'react'
import { Form } from 'reactstrap'

const Login = () => {
  return (
    <Form>
      <FormGroup>
    <Label for="exampleEmail">
      Email
    </Label>
    <Input
      id="exampleEmail"name="email"placeholder="with a placeholder"type="email"/>
  </FormGroup>
    </Form>
  )
}

export default Login
